OL,3,CRuben Amorim says 'decision will be
OL,4,Cmade' on Manchester United move this
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,FChris Hall reports from Old Trafford
OL,9,FRuben Amorim has promised to clarify
OL,10,Fhis future after Sporting Lisbon play
OL,11,Fon Friday evening as a move to
OL,12,FManchester United edges closer.
OL,14,FAfter deciding to sack their manager
OL,15,FErik Ten Hag, United immediately set
OL,16,Ftheir sights on highly-rated coach
OL,17,FAmorim, who is preparing to lead
OL,18,FSporting against Estrela da Amadora in
OL,19,Fthe Primeira Liga on Friday 1 November.
