OL,7,FThe club informed Sporting that they
OL,8,Fwould meet the 39-year-old's 10
OL,9,Fmillion euros (#8.4m) release clause,
OL,10,Fand in a statement to Portugal's
OL,11,Ffinancial regulator the club said that
OL,12,F"Manchester United FC has expressed an
OL,13,Finterest in hiring coach Ruben Amorim."
OL,15,FAt a pre-match press conference,
OL,16,FAmorim was peppered with questions
OL,17,Fabout his prospective switch to the
OL,18,FPremier League but remained tight-
OL,19,Flipped.
