OL,3,CRuben Amorim says 'decision will be
OL,4,Cmade' on Manchester United move this
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,FHe said: "It is a negotiation between
OL,8,Ftwo clubs. It's never easy. Even with
OL,9,Fthe clauses it's never easy, they have
OL,10,Fto talk.
OL,12,F"We will have clarification after the
OL,13,Fgame. It will be very clear, so it's
OL,14,Fone more day. After the game tomorrow,
OL,15,Fwe will have the decision made."
OL,17,FAsked what he liked about the Premier
OL,18,FLeague as he prepared to leave the
OL,19,Fpress conference, he said with a
OL,20,Fsmile: "Everything".
