OL,7,FA deal is reportedly close to being
OL,8,Fannounced, with reports saying a deal
OL,9,Funtil 2027, with the option of a
OL,10,Ffurther season, has been agreed.
OL,12,FAmorim's first match as United manager
OL,13,Fis not expected to come until the
OL,14,FNovember 24 trip to promoted Ipswich.
OL,16,FThe 39-year-old is preparing to lead
OL,17,FSporting in three more games,
OL,18,Fincluding Tuesday's Champions League
OL,19,Fclash with Manchester City ` a club he
OL,20,Fhas been linked to as Pep Guardiola
OL,21,Fponders his future.
