OL,7,FIn recent weeks, he has been suggested
OL,8,Fas a future Manchester City manager,
OL,9,Fwith Sporting's Hugo Viana, a close
OL,10,Ffriend, due to move to the blue half
OL,11,Fof Manchester as the club's new
OL,12,Fdirector of football next season.
OL,14,FSunday's controversial 2-1 defeat at
OL,15,FWest Ham, in which Jarrod Bowen's
OL,16,Fdisputed late penalty proved decisive,
OL,17,Fwas the final straw for Ten Hag.
