OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,FSpeaking on Thursday 31 November,
OL,8,FHammers boss Julen Lopetegui said: "I
OL,9,Fwish the best for (Ten Hag). He did
OL,10,Fvery good work and he's a very good
OL,11,Fcoach. I understand these kind of
OL,12,Fmoments. I'm sure that very soon he is
OL,13,Fgoing to be working again, for sure."
OL,15,FA club statement read: "Erik ten Hag
OL,16,Fhas left his role as Manchester United
OL,17,Fmen's first-team manager. Erik was
OL,18,Fappointed in April 2022 and led the
OL,19,Fclub to two domestic trophies, winning
OL,20,Fthe Carabao Cup in 2023 and the FA Cup
OL,21,Fin 2024.
